reviewText: REAL HOT SEXY BABIES... HIGHLY RECOMMANDED !!!

I luuuuuv Jun! This DVD, like the rest of the series is pretty weak for the most part, but what saves it is Jun. Unlike the other DVDs in this line Jun actually has some meat on her bones and actually posses a figure. Be warned, the soundtrack to this reaks like day old colored greens! Get some CDs, because you must play this DVD with the mute button.
Also, there is no nudity and its not some fetish thing. She just walks around and junk. Its like one of those fish-tank or fireplace DVDs, execept that its a woman, and she looks good. And your buddies won't call you a yuppie.
